work.summary:
Member of the Nexans TMA team and responsible for the .NET scope.
My mission mainly consists in analyzing the needs of the customers and in proposing adequate technical solutions.
I am in particular responsible for the Connected Drums application, which is a GPS tracking application for Nexans cable drums.
Tools:
- Azure IoT hub;
- Azure DevOps;
- AspNet Web API;
- Azure functions;
- Angular 5.
